WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.520
Hi, I just wanted to tell you another

00:00:01.979 --> 00:00:07.500
dream I had a while back that

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:09.960
I want to get out there. I want to get

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:11.940
this on the web to let people

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:13.980
pray over this. I don't know if this is

00:00:11.940 --> 00:00:15.899
during the tribulation that this happens

00:00:13.980 --> 00:00:18.000
or if this happens before the

00:00:15.900 --> 00:00:19.920
tribulation, but

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.480
you know, it's part of the birthing pains

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:27.359
that happen. In this dream,

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:30.180
there's a massive asteroid and it's

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:32.460
coming into the Earth. I see it

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:35.460
and everybody can see it, but you could

00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:38.640
hear it; it sounded like massive

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:41.219
freight trains. Everything was

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:43.739
shaking and moving so fast. I went

00:00:41.219 --> 00:00:46.320
outside in the dream and looked up, and

00:00:43.739 --> 00:00:48.660
it's just a massive streak of light, a

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:51.539
fireball coming out of the sky. It

00:00:48.660 --> 00:00:54.000
was moving so quick and so fast that it

00:00:51.539 --> 00:00:56.460
sounded like the whole earth was shaking.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.719
It was incredible; this thing

00:00:56.460 --> 00:01:04.080
was humongous. In the dream,

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:07.380
the United States tried to

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:09.840
shoot it down with a laser beam. It

00:01:07.380 --> 00:01:12.600
was moving too quick to shoot it down

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:15.900
with a rocket, so they used this laser

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:18.720
beam that, in my dream, was green. They hit

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:22.140
it with this laser weapon

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:25.920
and it split the rock. This

00:01:22.140 --> 00:01:28.320
massive asteroid split in two and

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:31.080
it busted up one half

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:34.380
into little bitty fragments, but the

00:01:31.080 --> 00:01:37.259
other half was still massive. It hit

00:01:34.380 --> 00:01:41.100
by the islands, by San Juan, Puerto

00:01:37.259 --> 00:01:44.040
Rico, and the Bahamas—all that

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:46.740
area out there. When it did, it

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:50.899
crashed into the ocean and created

00:01:46.740 --> 00:01:55.079
this massive tsunami. I'm talking

00:01:50.899 --> 00:01:58.079
humongous, like 100 feet up

00:01:55.079 --> 00:02:01.320
or more. It was moving so

00:01:58.079 --> 00:02:03.179
quick and so fast; it covered the islands

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:04.979
up. It covered Haiti; it

00:02:03.180 --> 00:02:06.780
covered those things up.

00:02:04.979 --> 00:02:09.538
It just went over the top of

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:11.879
them. I could see it in the dream;

00:02:09.538 --> 00:02:14.458
these islands were just completely

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:16.560
engulfed with water.

00:02:14.459 --> 00:02:19.140
It went clear into Africa.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:22.319
When it came into

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:25.859
America, because it was so close, it hit

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:28.079
Miami, North Carolina, and South Carolina—all

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:31.260
that area.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:33.540
But the main area that I

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:36.480
was shown in the dream was the Miami

00:02:33.540 --> 00:02:39.359
area and Fort Lauderdale. It went

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:40.560
inland like the one that hit

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:43.379
Japan; the tsunami

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:45.180
wave

00:02:43.379 --> 00:02:47.518
washed in and

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:49.739
just wiped out houses and

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:52.739
buildings like they were nothing. It just

00:02:49.739 --> 00:02:55.200
blew them down. There were

00:02:52.739 --> 00:02:57.959
millions of people who were in

00:02:55.200 --> 00:03:00.720
trouble and lost. Many were dead, and the

00:02:57.959 --> 00:03:02.940
Lord had me praying. When I woke up

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:05.940
the next day, He had me praying for these

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:07.560
people that they would hear Him and that

00:03:05.940 --> 00:03:09.359
they would not be there at that time—that

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:10.980
they would leave if this is

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:13.379
something that was going to happen soon.

00:03:10.980 --> 00:03:16.799
I don't know, but I prayed for these people so

00:03:13.379 --> 00:03:17.579
they would get out of harm's way.

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:22.739
It was just something that was very...

00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:25.739
when you wake up, you're in a

00:03:22.739 --> 00:03:29.280
cold sweat because it shook me. I was like,

00:03:25.739 --> 00:03:30.959
'Lord, I have to tell

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:34.080
people about this,'but I've just prayed

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:35.940
over it. I could

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:37.860
see that it was going to happen, and I don't

00:03:35.940 --> 00:03:40.799
know if we can stop it or

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:43.319
prevent it or whatever. I just felt in

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:45.840
my heart, this massive tsunami,

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:48.480
this massive asteroid coming out of the

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:50.220
sky. I've looked online at the

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:52.260
NASA site to see, but they

00:03:50.220 --> 00:03:55.319
didn't know this was coming. They didn't

00:03:52.260 --> 00:03:57.420
announce it on TV; they

00:03:55.319 --> 00:03:59.518
didn't tell people that it was coming. It

00:03:57.420 --> 00:04:02.819
just happened and, like I

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:04.980
said, it was humongous. It flew in and

00:04:02.819 --> 00:04:08.399
hit out there in the ocean, in

00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:10.920
the Atlantic. It caused

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:12.420
devastation worldwide. I

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:14.700
don't know if this is the Tribulation the Lord is

00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:16.978
showing me, or if it's something

00:04:14.700 --> 00:04:18.478
that happens in the birthing pains, but

00:04:16.978 --> 00:04:20.399
it's just one of the things I felt like

00:04:18.478 --> 00:04:23.340
I should share that the Lord has shown

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:24.539
me. Thank you very much for watching. There are

00:04:23.340 --> 00:04:25.979
other things that the Lord

00:04:24.540 --> 00:04:27.780
showed me, and I'm going to tell those in

00:04:25.979 --> 00:04:30.020
other videos. Have a blessed

00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:30.020
day. Bye.

